{"tid":416113,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"果汁發泡酒同好請入","createTime":"2017-09-27T13:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T13:32:56.000Z","uid":126221,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe9f03341f4ba60c9e8ceced232d3c4bec1ac0c","tid":416113,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:48:59.000Z","msg":"有無巴打都喜歡飲呢類酒？<br />\n以前喜歡飲 Kirin 既冰結系列，而家就飲多左 Suntory 既 ほろよい (Horoyoi)。<br />\n因為香港好少見果味冰結(原味檸檬唔計)，反而間唔中響百佳有得賣 ほろよい。"},{"pid":"a2790fc3d97324bcb64eee559c83aab30fdcadea","tid":416113,"uid":54563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:31:31.000Z","msg":"之前一田買過プレミアムほろよい青提味幾好飲<br />\n之後掃咗幾隻味 覺得除咗西柚之外其他都幾好飲<br />\n不過我覺得一田無Sale果時賣好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a291bbb705275c5de36e407431537466a7110cad","tid":416113,"uid":109694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:34:01.000Z","msg":"ほろよい momo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734f3713d32a0441a1679deb7ccc144dfdafbc4a","tid":416113,"uid":82717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:42:43.000Z","msg":"La Marca 算唔算？價錢夠平"},{"pid":"c4d50f307519424eeecb5a18d795dfe609eb580c","tid":416113,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T13:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>La Marca 算唔算？價錢夠平</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢隻唔係 Spark Wine 黎咩 ?<br />\n不過重點係 ... 咩價錢先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f520a73c73e59eee0210c69a90ae23c35e0d52","tid":416113,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前一田買過プレミアムほろよい青提味幾好飲<br />\n之後掃咗幾隻味 覺得除咗西柚之外其他都幾好飲<br />\n不過我覺得一田無Sale果時賣好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問 Premium 版賣緊幾錢呢？之前響日本好似無見過。"}]}